    "name": "Generate and publish Instagram Reels with Gemini and Veo",
    "views": 519,
    "recentViews": 1,
    "totalViews": 519,
    "createdAt": "2026-02-01T09:34:07.470Z",
    "description": "### How it Works\n\n* The workflow runs automatically on a schedule (daily at a set time).\n* It defines the video topic, caption, and aspect ratio.\n* Gemini generates a detailed visual prompt for a short-form vertical video.\n* Google Veo creates the video based on that prompt.\n* The finished video is published to Instagram as a Reel with the preset caption.\n\n---\n\n### Set-up Steps\n\n* Connect Google Gemini and Veo API credentials.\n* Authenticate Instagram publishing access.\n* Customize the video topic, caption, and posting schedule.\n* Run a quick test to verify everything works.\n\n**Estimated setup time:** ~20–40 minutes.\n",
